{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840480507,"sessionID":"ses_287a9e322ffeNAC5ZIgQUZgpZk","part":{"id":"prt_d785744ea001ARejHrc6pN7ALg","messageID":"msg_d7857368f001HZ1tBrtj7qTX1J","sessionID":"ses_287a9e322ffeNAC5ZIgQUZgpZk","type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Based on the proposal.md, I need to implement AR-003 by:\n\n1. **Updating `doc.go`** - Add package-level documentation about shared types\n2. **Updating `types.go`** - Add comments marking which types are shared vs CRD-specific\n3. **Updating `validation.go`** - Extract shared validation functions with public APIs\n4. **Adding tests** for the new shared validation functions\n\nLet me implement these changes:","time":{"start":1775840480505,"end":1775840480505}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840492482,"sessionID":"ses_287a9e322ffeNAC5ZIgQUZgpZk","part":{"id":"prt_d78574cfa001thuSVS2sCX14fb","messageID":"msg_d7857368f001HZ1tBrtj7qTX1J","sessionID":"ses_287a9e322ffeNAC5ZIgQUZgpZk","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_2c282ab31a36437795899b6f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go","oldString":"// Package v1alpha1 contains API types for the AgentRuntime CRD.\n// +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n// +versionName=v1alpha1\npackage v1alpha1","newString":"// Package v1alpha1 defines the AgentCube runtime API types.\n//\n// Shared Types:\n// Types without AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter prefix are intended for reuse across CRDs:\n//   - ResourceQuota: Resource limits and requests (CPU, Memory, Storage)\n//   - NetworkPolicy/NetworkRule: Network access control rules\n//   - LifecycleHook: Lifecycle callbacks (PreStart, PostStop)\n//   - ContainerSpec: Container configuration (image, command, args, env)\n//   - AgentRuntimeCondition: Generic condition pattern for status reporting\n//\n// CRD-Specific Types:\n// Types prefixed with AgentRuntime or CodeInterpreter are specific\n// to those CRDs and should not be assumed reusable:\n//   - AgentRuntime, AgentRuntimeSpec, AgentRuntimeStatus, AgentRuntimeList\n//   - AgentRuntimePhase, AgentRuntimeConditionType\n//   - CodeInterpreterSpec\n//\n// Validation:\n// Shared validation functions are provided for reusable types:\n//   - ValidateResourceQuota: Validates resource quota fields\n//   - ValidateNetworkPolicy: Validates network policy configuration\n//   - ValidateContainerSpec: Validates container specification\n//   - ValidateLifecycleHook: Validates lifecycle hook URLs\n//\n// Example usage for new CRDs:\n//\n//\ttype MyCRDSpec struct {\n//\t    Resources *ResourceQuota      `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n//\t    Network   *NetworkPolicy      `json:\"network,omitempty\"`\n//\t    Container ContainerSpec       `json:\"container,omitempty\"`\n//\t}\n//\n//\tfunc ValidateMyCRD(spec *MyCRDSpec) field.ErrorList {\n//\t    allErrs := field.ErrorList{}\n//\t    allErrs = append(allErrs, ValidateResourceQuota(spec.Resources, field.NewPath(\"resources\"))...)\n//\t    allErrs = append(allErrs, ValidateNetworkPolicy(spec.Network, field.NewPath(\"network\"))...)\n//\t    allErrs = append(allErrs, ValidateContainerSpec(&spec.Container, field.NewPath(\"container\"))...)\n//\t    return allErrs\n//\t}\n//\n// +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n// +versionName=v1alpha1\npackage v1alpha1"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/defaults.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation_test.go":[]},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go\n==================