stValidateAgentRuntimeStatusUpdate_ValidTransitions\n--- PASS: TestValidateAgentRuntimeStatusUpdate_ValidTransitions (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateAgentRuntimePhase\n--- PASS: TestValidateAgentRuntimePhase (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_Nil\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_Nil (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_Valid\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_Valid (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_InvalidImage\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_InvalidImage (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_ValidImageNotEnabled\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_ValidImageNotEnabled (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_InvalidResources\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_InvalidResources (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_EmptyImage\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_EmptyImage (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestValidateCodeInterpreter_ValidImageFormats\n--- PASS: TestValidateCodeInterpreter_ValidImageFormats (0.00s)\nPASS\nok  \tgithub.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\t0.007s\n","exit":0,"description":"Run tests for the v1alpha1 package","truncated":false},"title":"Run tests for the v1alpha1 package","time":{"start":1775840655459,"end":1775840656451}}}}
